e of contents\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"><\/i><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-toc__toggle-button elementor-toc__toggle-button--collapse\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"elementor-toc__fd3cef9\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-label=\"Close table of contents\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-up\"><\/i><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div id=\"elementor-toc__fd3cef9\" class=\"elementor-toc__body\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-toc__spinner-container\">\n\t\t\t\t<i class=\"elementor-toc__spinner eicon-animation-spin eicon-loading\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><\/i>\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9aa16ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9aa16ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.18.0 - 20-12-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"509\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-927629-768x509-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-21038\" alt=\"Tobias Dziuba\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-927629-768x509-1.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-927629-768x509-1-300x199.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3062d3d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3062d3d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Over the years, there have been several updates and changes strike the platform that only enhanced its popularity all across the globe. Among the fraternity of social media marketers, Facebook is still the best bet with most of their ad spending drive towards the same.<\/p><p class=\"look\">A recent study indicates that over 90% of marketers agree that they use Facebook on a daily basis. This means around 3 million businesses are hooked on Facebook to achieve their marketing objectives.<\/p><p class=\"look\">If you\u2019re looking to yield the best reap out of your Facebook marketing efforts and budget, you can\u2019t afford to miss these proven Facebook marketing tips that are being appreciated by the world\u2019s top digital marketers.<\/p><p>So, let\u2019s take a look at them one by one.<\/p><h2 id=\"pick-the-right-business-category-for-your-page\">Pick The Right Business Category for Your Page<\/h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4fc34d4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4fc34d4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Always keep in mind that you need a business page and not a personal page.<br \/>While creating your business, make sure you choose the right category for your business page.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9427d8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d9427d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"509\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-936137-768x509-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-21039\" alt=\"Business\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-936137-768x509-1.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-936137-768x509-1-300x199.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ceb7d70 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ceb7d70\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">This affects your further conversations to some extent. For example, if you pick a local business category, you will have to add a physical location for the same while that won\u2019t be the case with an e-commerce business.<br \/>Please note that in most cases, local business is a common choice.<\/p><h3 id=\"work-on-your-photos\">Work On Your Photos<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a7da82 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7a7da82\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Don\u2019t take this point lightly as it needs serious consideration.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7cc3c75 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7cc3c75\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2530775-683x1024-1-200x300.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-21040\" alt=\"Girl\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2530775-683x1024-1-200x300.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2530775-683x1024-1.jpeg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31fbebf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"31fbebf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Make sure you upload high-quality photos on your profile. From choosing the product photos to the cover photo, each and every graphic element should be in sync.<br \/>Your profile\u2019s cover pic need not have a\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.crazyegg.com\/blog\/call-to-action-examples\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Call-To-Action<\/a>\u00a0(CTA) but you can exhibit your creative edge on this.<\/p><p class=\"look\">As a value-driven businessman or marketer, you shouldn\u2019t lose this opportunity to amplify your brand presence over the web.<\/p><p><strong>Also Check<\/strong>\u00a0:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/facebook-page-promotion\/\">How To Promote A Facebook Business Page?<\/a><\/p><h3 id=\"prefer-custom-facebook-tabs\">Prefer Custom Facebook Tabs<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c43487 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8c43487\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Can you recall the small-sized sidebar tabs on your profile? Do you know you can customize them? Let\u2019s know why:<\/p><p><strong>\u2022 You can add any and all relevant information regarding your brand.<br \/>\u2022 You can use it as an option to feature a CTA.<br \/>\u2022 It helps reply to questions that users might have before they go further.<\/strong><\/p><p class=\"look\"><br \/>There are different tabs with names like About, Events, Photos, Videos, Posts, Groups and others.<br \/>Consider them as entry points to your website. For example, you can use the CTA \u201cSign Up\u201d to invite visitors to register on your website.<\/p><p class=\"look\">Always remember that the prime motive is to engage with the target audience.<\/p><h3 id=\"upload-videos-on-facebook-directly-rather-the-inserting-a-youtube-video\">Upload Videos on Facebook Directly Rather the Inserting a YouTube Video<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9398385 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9398385\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2510422-1024x683-1.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-21041\" alt=\"Men making video\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2510422-1024x683-1.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2510422-1024x683-1-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-2510422-1024x683-1-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-146c1bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"146c1bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">When posting video content, it is suggested to upload the video file directly on Facebook rather than embedding a YouTube video URL. Learn some\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/facebook-post-ideas\/\">catchy Facebook post ideas<\/a>.<\/p><h3 id=\"pick-your-cta-knob\">Pick Your CTA Knob<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1553f17 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1553f17\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">On every Facebook business page, there is a small CTA button. For example, just below the cover pic, you\u2019ll find a CTA button like \u201cSign UP\u201d There could be different CTA options like \u2022 Book Now \u2022 Contact Us \u2022 Use App \u2022 Play Game \u2022 Shop Now \u2022 Sign Up \u2022 Watch Video \u00a0 The best way to use them is to redirect a user to a landing page when he or she clicks on it. There are no predefined rules for this category, but it is always a good option to make an optimum.<\/p><h3 id=\"pursue-the-70-20-10-approach\">Pursue The \u201c70-20-10\u201d Approach<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc04fb8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fc04fb8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">After you\u2019re done with generating engagement on your page, content is the next step you should work on.<br \/>There is no fixed rule and you can always try out different formats. For example, you start with a small business updated followed by visual content.<br \/>To establish a perfect balance of the content you\u2019re supposed to post on your page, it is advised to follow the 70-20-10 rule which means:<\/p><ul><li>Publish original content 70% of the time.<\/li><li>\u00a0Publish content pertinent to your followers\u2019 interests 20% of the time.<\/li><li>\u00a0Prefer self-promotional content 10% of the time.<\/li><\/ul><h3 id=\"declutter-your-posts\">Declutter Your Posts<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8035f35 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8035f35\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-4946703-683x1024-1-200x300.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-21042\" alt=\"Declutter Your Posts\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-4946703-683x1024-1-200x300.jpeg 200w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/pexels-photo-4946703-683x1024-1.jpeg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0d17b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c0d17b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Cleaning up your posts could allow you to lend a leaner look to your page that makes it rank above the rest. A compelling social media post along with good quality visuals is 10 times more likely to generate engagement than a plain text post. Prefer using sharp quality images and in case of a link post, make sure you eliminate the link URL from the post copy.<\/p><h3 id=\"share-user-generated-content\">Share User-Generated Content<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-debb5f1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"debb5f1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">If you think you\u2019re falling short of your own content, you can choose to share user-generated content on your page. This is found to be a good strategy to encourage brand loyalty and make users feel included on your page.<\/p><h3 id=\"if-possible-post-live-videos\">If Possible, Post LIVE Videos<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4dc8e52 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4dc8e52\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">One promising way to boost engagement is to post video content. Videos are found to get a fabulous response on Facebook. Do you know a majority of users watch Facebook videos with the sound off? So, don\u2019t forget to caption your videos to boost engagement. It will augment video watching time by an average of 12%. If there is a big event happening near your place, start sharing it with your fan base on Facebook live. You can use your smartphone and broadcast the video live on Facebook.<\/p><p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/instagram-reels\/\">Instagram Reels<\/a><\/p><h3 id=\"analyze-your-posts-using-facebook-insights\">Analyze Your Posts Using Facebook Insights<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d88843 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4d88843\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Improvement is surely an intrinsic part of Facebook marketing. The best way to support this is to monitor your content using Facebook analytics. You can get to various things this way like Page likes, post reach, and engagement etc.<\/p><h3 id=\"examine-your-timing\">Examine Your Timing<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9111b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d9111b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">\u200bBy utilizing your Facebook insights data, you can figure out what types of posts work best and at what time. This would help you schedule your posts at times when they\u2019re more likely to engage. During peak hours, you can do a lot of experiments with your content options.<\/p><h3 id=\"to-analyze-user-behavior-prefer-audience-insights\">To Analyze User Behavior, Prefer Audience Insights<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64e1dfc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"64e1dfc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">For more details on the audience you\u2019re targeting, you can refer to audience insights under Facebook insights. This would allow you to find information like age and gender breakdowns, education levels, and job descriptions. You can also find out the hobbies and interests of your followers.\u00a0<\/p><p class=\"look\"><strong>Also Read:\u00a0<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/smm-packages\/facebook-marketing-packages-india\/\">How Much Does It Cost To Advertise on Facebook<\/a><\/p><h3 id=\"promote-your-posts-using-facebook-ads\">Promote Your Posts Using Facebook Ads<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7460138 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7460138\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"700\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Facebook-Ads-768x700-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-21043\" alt=\"Facebook Ads\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Facebook-Ads-768x700-1.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Facebook-Ads-768x700-1-300x273.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46fdcb9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"46fdcb9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Be it a short-term campaign or you wish to give that much-needed initial push to your page, Facebook ads could be a great way to attract more followers. And you would be happier to know that Facebook ads are much cheaper than Google Adwords.<\/p><h3 id=\"filter-your-audience-for-maximum-reach-of-your-ads\">Filter Your Audience for Maximum Reach of Your Ads<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1ddeb5f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1ddeb5f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">If you surely wish to ensure that\u00a0your Facebook Ads are effective, make no delay in learning how to narrow your audience. You can choose from location-specific audiences to segmentation based on interests and hobbies. For example, if you\u2019re a magician, you can target your audience in a particular area.<\/p><h3 id=\"take-your-efforts-beyond-facebook\">Take Your Efforts Beyond Facebook<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2c91780 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2c91780\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Though internal promotion can be easily done on Facebook, it is also a good idea to think about bringing traffic to your Facebook page. By relying on promoted posts and paid ads, you can target Facebook users who are new to the platform.<\/p><h3 id=\"double-your-efforts-with-influencers\">Double Your Efforts with Influencers<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68bda5a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"68bda5a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">If you\u2019re finding it hard to boost engagement on Facebook, there is no harm in partnering with experts. Influencer marketing is always a great idea to step up your engagement efforts. There are many&nbsp;social media management tools&nbsp;available that allow you to find them. You can reach out to Twitter, Linked In with influencer marketing and promote your Facebook page there.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"schedule-an-easy-content-to-boost-engagement\">Schedule An Easy Content to Boost Engagement<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01fc66f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"01fc66f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Don\u2019t go for a big one but plan a smaller one with some gratification. Running a contest on Facebook is a great way to support your organic promotion efforts while promoting engagement with users. You can gratify your users with a gift voucher or a free product sample.<\/p><h3 id=\"prefer-short-engaging-video-posts\">Prefer Short, Engaging Video Posts<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f916283 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f916283\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Video-Posts-1024x683-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-21044\" alt=\"Video Posts\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Video-Posts-1024x683-1.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Video-Posts-1024x683-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Video-Posts-1024x683-1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da81fc7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"da81fc7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">People have started loving videos over long-text posts. To drive engagement, create short but enticing video posts that people find worthy to share with others. There are many tools available online that allow you to create such interesting video posts.<\/p><h3 id=\"humanize-your-brand-with-fun-loaded-photos\">Humanize Your Brand with Fun-Loaded Photos<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c158506 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c158506\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">Establishing a human connection is intrinsic to Facebook and one should never forget it. As a brand, you can carry forward this notion by publishing photos that show your employees in a humorous and relevant way.<\/p><h3 id=\"use-emojis-for-facebook-marketing\">Use Emojis for Facebook Marketing<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0edfbf9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0edfbf9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">According to a study, over 90% of users prefer using emojis as they feel that they are the best reflection of their feelings. The emojis of animals, babies and expressions are immensely popular in the Facebook community.<\/p><h3 id=\"clone-your-primary-revenue-sourcing-audience\">Clone Your Primary Revenue-Sourcing Audience<\/h3>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e456bde elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e456bde\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"look\">To boost up your relevant audiences, cloning your best-performing audience is a good strategy. Count on Facebook\u2019s Lookalike Audience feature and expand your reach to a new audience that features similar attributes. It is very much easy and effective.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0229dc7 content-align-ct